name: Akash Aryal
about: Hi! My name is Akash Aryal. I am currently a freshmen at Cornell University majoring in CS in the college of Arts and Science. I'm currently interested in web and app development (both front and back end). I am most familiar with mysql and laravel but am looking to expand my stack to incorporate React and nosql dbms. In my free time I enjoy playing tennis, getting flamed in league, and lots of anime...lots.
